items.name: AUTO
desc: If there is enough space to put them side by side, this arrangement is preferred. If the descriptions would overlap when arranged side by side, they are staggered.

items.name: SIDE_BY_SIDE
desc: The descriptions are arranged side by side.

items.name: STAGGER_EVEN
desc: The descriptions are alternately put on two lines with the even values out of the normal line.

items.name: STAGGER_ODD
desc: The descriptions are alternately put on two lines with the odd values out of the normal line.
